    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Contamination of the unconsolidated material on the earth's surface formed by the weathering of rock and that portion of the earth's surface that can support plant life.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
